  npcName: "Offrundel K\u0148ourbastien"
  dialogueLines:
  - "When the Core weakens, the world doesn\u2019t end immediately."
  - "It waits.\nLike it\u2019s expecting something."
  - We never figured out what it was waiting for.
  - 'Check out the recipe page in your inventory..

    You might find something
    new there!'
  recipesToUnlock:
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: f0c535d535ee3ad40b718f2509ca7e6e, type: 2}
  ambientDialogue:
  - Dig. Wait. Dig. Wait. The rhythm never changes.
  - "I buried my name a long time ago. Don\u2019t ask for it."
  - "The Core isn't sleeping. It\u2019s holding its breath."
  - "My lantern sees things my eyes don\u2019t. Be careful."
